other_data.1: For the species Loxodonta africana, 22 of the total 30 properties (73%) have three or more annual population estimates between 1903 and 2024 which allows for robust trend estimation with General Additive Models. Furthermore, 2 of the total 30 properties (7%) have two annual population estimates between 1903 and 2024 and we fitted Poisson log linear curves to join the two population estimates and estimate trends. These properties are: Blaauwbosch Private Game Reserve, Rietspruit Game Reserve. Finally, 6 of the total 30 properties (20%) have only one population estimates between 1903 and 2024 and so were excluded from the analysis. These properties are: Dan - Property01, Hopewell Private Game Reserve, Kwazulu, my_property, test 061023, testing
